data.description: ***Seller is willing to contribute to buyer buydown on interest rate.  Please inquire.  Located at end of cul de sac, this beautiful 4 bedroom, 2 bath brick home is move in ready. Granite counter tops, stainless steel appliances, open floor plan, with one bedroom on separate side of home. Large living area, easy to place furniture, decorations, plants to create your cozy atmosphere.  Wall of windows in living and dining area offering natural light.  Tranquil large backyard over looking pond, your own getaway.  Community pool and playgrounds. OPEN HOUSE Sunday Nov 12th 10am-1pm
